ğŸ“Œ 5ï¸âƒ£ Security Concepts

Security Groups

Virtual firewall for EC2 instances

Controls inbound & outbound traffic

Example rules:

Type	Port	Source	Purpose
SSH	22	My IP	Connect to server
HTTP	80	Anywhere	Websites

NACLs (Network ACLs)

Subnet-level firewall

Stateless

